---
// AboutPageStory.astro — timeline/journey format
// Inspired by Vidyard: alternating image/text blocks with milestone markers
// DRAFT COPY — update with Feldon's own words once received (Section 12 of info.md)
---

<section class="story" aria-label="Feldon's story and journey">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="story-header fade-in">
      <p class="eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        My journey
      </p>
      <h2 class="story-h2">Where I came from.<br>And why I coach.</h2>
      <p class="story-sub">
        A story that starts earlier than most. And gets more honest along the way.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline wrapper -->
    <div class="timeline">

      <!-- Milestone 1: The beginning — text left, image right -->
      <div class="milestone fade-in">
        <div class="milestone-text">
          <span class="milestone-tag">The start</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-h3">I didn't wait for permission.</h3>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            I started my first business when most people my age were still figuring out
            what they wanted to study. That was a choice, and it came with everything
            you'd expect. The excitement. The mistakes. The moments of genuine
            progress, and the moments where it all felt like it was going backwards.
          </p>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            Born in September 2002 and raised in the West Midlands, this community
            has always been part of how I think and operate.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-visual">
          <img
            src="/Images/feldon-haynes-seated-portrait.webp"
            alt="Feldon Haynes seated in a professional portrait"
            width="480"
            height="380"
            loading="lazy"
            class="milestone-img milestone-img--portrait"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline connector -->
      <div class="timeline-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="connector-line"></div>
        <div class="connector-dot"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Milestone 2: Building and failing — text left, image right -->
      <div class="milestone milestone--reverse fade-in">
        <div class="milestone-text">
          <span class="milestone-tag">The real bit</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-h3">35 businesses. Not all of them worked.</h3>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            I've now started 35 businesses. They haven't all worked. That's the bit
            most coaches won't tell you. But it's also the bit that matters most.
            Because you don't get real business knowledge from the ones that went
            smoothly. You get it from figuring out what went wrong and what you'd
            do differently.
          </p>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            The West Midlands is where I grew up, where I built my businesses, and
            where I'm based now. I've worked with the Black Country Chamber of
            Commerce, delivered workshops at the University of Warwick Science Park,
            and spent time in rooms with people who are trying to build something real.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-visual">
          <img
            src="/Images/feldon-haynes-whiteboard-strategy-session.webp"
            alt="Feldon Haynes mapping a client strategy on a whiteboard"
            width="480"
            height="380"
            loading="lazy"
            class="milestone-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline connector -->
      <div class="timeline-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="connector-line"></div>
        <div class="connector-dot"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Milestone 3: Coaching — text left, image right -->
      <div class="milestone fade-in">
        <div class="milestone-text">
          <span class="milestone-tag">Why I coach</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-h3">I got tired of watching talented people get stuck.</h3>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            When I started coaching, it wasn't a pivot or a next step. It came from
            watching talented, motivated people get stuck in exactly the same places.
            Not because they lacked ability, but because no one had helped them turn
            what was in their head into a structured plan.
          </p>
          <p class="milestone-body">
            That's what I do. And that's why I do it.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://calendly.com/feldeluxe/discovery-call"
            class="milestone-cta"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Book a free call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2.5 7h9M8 3.5L11.5 7 8 10.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-visual">
          <img
            src="/Images/feldon-haynes-sales-funnel-training.webp"
            alt="Feldon Haynes presenting coaching frameworks on a whiteboard"
            width="480"
            height="380"
            loading="lazy"
            class="milestone-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: #FAF9F6;
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  /* Header */
  .story-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #534AB7;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .eyebrow-line {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: #F2D832;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .story-h2 {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #1a1744;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .story-sub {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #7e7a9f;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 1060px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Each milestone: two-column image + text */
  .milestone {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 48px 0;
  }
  .milestone--reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }
  .milestone--reverse > * {
    direction: ltr;
  }

  /* Milestone text */
  .milestone-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #534AB7;
    background: #EEEDFE;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .milestone-h3 {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #1a1744;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .milestone-body {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #5a5680;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .milestone-body:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .milestone-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    color: #534AB7;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #F2D832;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .milestone-cta:hover { color: #3b309e; }

  /* Image */
  .milestone-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 340px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 30%;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EEEDFE 0%, #e3dfff 100%);
  }
  .milestone-img--portrait {
    object-position: center 15%;
  }

  /* Timeline connectors */
  .timeline-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .connector-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #EEEDFE, #534AB7);
  }
  .connector-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #534AB7;
    border: 3px solid #FAF9F6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #534AB7;
  }

  /* ── Tablet ──────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .milestone {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
      direction: ltr;
      padding: 32px 0;
    }
    .milestone--reverse { direction: ltr; }
    .milestone-img { height: 260px; }
    .story-h2 { font-size: 34px; }
    .milestone-h3 { font-size: 24px; }
    .timeline-connector { display: none; }
  }

  /* ── Mobile ──────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .story { padding: 52px 0; }
    .story-h2 { font-size: 26px; }
    .story-header { margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .milestone { padding: 24px 0; gap: 20px; }
    .milestone-img { height: 220px; }
    .milestone-h3 { font-size: 20px; }
  }
</style>
